_sText:
Hey Guys, Just made an account since I thought I would upload my creations. Already spent alot of time on this site and I enjoyed most of the stuff here.

About this map:

I made this map by myself, got the idea from other BreakBox maps and I feeled like making one myself;

The box in the middle of the map spawns HeGrenades when damaged and will eventually break apart.
In the middle of the water lies a fully ammo'ed up p228 for the one that likes to dive.
Once you fall into the water u can't return all the way to the top anymore but you Can climb up two 'hiding' spots.
The rest is pretty straightforward i guess. 
O ye, the map is bot proof! It's actually fun to play with bots in this one:)

That was it, I hope you enjoy it!

Cya; Uvall94 - LvD
